text.tspan: URL Post Block reports redstone changes.
URL Post Block can also be right-clicked by user.
This is a very simple mod that opens the door to very complex things.
URL Post Wand reports target block data.
Using the URL Config Wand on Signs, Chests, Barrels, and Lecterns
Chests report full inventory contents when changed
Signs and Hanging Signs report front and back text
"device": block, wand, chest, barrel, lectern, signs
All URLium devices transmit these fields in addition to device-specific data:
URLium transmits redstone and block information over HTTP(S) to webservers.
